b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2334,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!","message":"<div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1626069600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer affected this time and her stats are described below.<\/div><div>Note: Unlocking an eligible adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Akasha (wind\/staff)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/0195f647529c185c878409ab5361c6212.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Akasha<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1fc4080420e16a67744809f28590c98b2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>967<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>561<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,228<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/19c706c3440276a68b516e5597e4e0c32.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Akashic Repose<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>6<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Restores HP to all allies, and continues<br>gradually healing over time.<br>Also, increases the entire team\'s strength,<br>and grants them overdamage.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Recovery Potency: 44<br>Skill Energy Required: 5,916<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 17,748<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +15%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 60 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbOverdamage<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 50%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 35<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c8617d88f15afc0758a831a32f276e572.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Vital Gate<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Creates a buff zone that lasts for 15 seconds<br>and gradually fills the skill gauges of adventurers<br>inside it. When placed, this buff zone will deal<br>damage to enemies, inflict stormlash, and restore<br>HP to the entire team relative to the amount of<br>damage dealt.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 900 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 15,000<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbSkill Charger<br>\\u30fbStormlash<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41<br>\\u30fbHP Drain<br>\\u3000\\u3000Recovers 20% of damage dealt<br>\\u3000\\u3000Recovers up to 100% of targeted unit\'s max HP<br>\\u3000\\u3000Target: Entire Team<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Recovery Potency +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases the potency of recovery skills by 20%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Wind) Above 10 Hits = Critical Rate +13%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Wind: <br>increases their critical rate by 13%<br>when the combo count is 10 or higher.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/24dc1983d110ed627df93dd3e6322d962.png\\"><\/span><span>Pursuer of Knowledge<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests.<br>In addition, using a skill will grant the user a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of two. After this amp is granted, this ability will<br>not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9d77939f4269ebb33ba6b5e2044474042.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Bog Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to bog by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted bog on them, their strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will<br>not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span><span>HP 70% = Healing +17%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases the potency of recovery skills by 17%<br>when HP is 70% or above.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1625983200,"prev_article_id":"2307","next_article_id":"2293","image_path":"","update_time":1625633686}}}'